    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and kept in absolutely stunning shape. It drives just as smooth as the day I brought it home, and honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish on it. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will appreciate how special it is. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014I promise it\u2019s even better in person!",
