      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, she\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept in truly spectacular shape. You know that feeling when you find a car that\u2019s been treated like a member of the family? That\u2019s this one. It drives like a dream and looks just as sharp as the day it rolled off the lot. There might be a tiny, barely-there mark if you really go looking for it, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as they come. I\u2019d love for this beauty to go to someone who will appreciate her as much as I have!",
